title: This 1 Bedroom Apartment Is The Perfect Place To Call Home!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'Welcome home to Quail Chase Apartments!', 'We offer quality & affordable 1, 2 & 3 bedroom apartments that you’ll surely love to call home.', 'We are in a great location and provide a community clubhouse with business center, an outdoor swimming pool, in-home washer & dryer rental program, updated turf field, new outdoor playground area & much more!', 'Here at Quail Chase, you’ll receive the quality & comfort you deserve.', 'All this combined with our professional on-site management & maintenance team, you can’t go wrong!', 'Give us a call today and come see for yourself.', 'Voucher Holders Welcome!*', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Sparkling Outdoor Swimming Pool', '- In-Home Washer & Dryer Rental Available!', '- On-Site Theater Room & Business Center', '- State-Of-The-Art Fitness Center', '- Updated Turf Field & Mail Kiosk', 'We are a pet-friendly community.', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Quail Chase participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $37,260 | 2 Occupants: $43,540 | 3 Occupants: $47,880 | 4 Occupants: $53,160 | 5 Occupants: $557,420 | 6 Occupants: $61,680.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:8:30AM-5:30PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', 'Quail Chase', '500 W. Airtex', 'Houston, TX, 77090', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'FZS1fi8X']
